{
  "stem": "22892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The dogs quit barking, so I knew that he was gone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when everything got quiet, in, you know-- I stuck my head out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was just nothing but lots of straw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Some of it's maybe a foot high, two feet, and then these huge stacks of straw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I got close to one of those stacks of straw and got closer to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I camouflaged myself real well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I thought and I'm going to-- you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it's like I'll just stay there, see what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "During the day I had no place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do because I was afraid to be in the open field.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Well after lunch, things were all over again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "This guy is back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I hear him talk to these people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the dogs are barking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then they're looking for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And, you know, and this went on for another-- I don't know-- a couple hours, and then quiet again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I had no idea whether it was dark or not because I didn't move.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I was hidden, just didn't move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I finally, thinking, you know, when they fed-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it's-- it just-- I don't remember exactly, the chicken or something they would call.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And, and I felt that it's getting dark or it's getting late, later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I thought I'll just maybe get out of there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I stuck my head out, and there was still some little daylight, not much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was getting darker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And there was a young woman came to get some straw with a pitchfork.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I stuck my head out just about the same time she started getting straw, and she saw me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I scared her to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
